---
title: Buttery Curried Coley with Roast Potatoes and Garlicky Broccoli
description: This Coley with Potatoes and Broccoli is deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/buttery-curried-coley-d1b62cd9-e9cb0906.jpg
